# Student Registration + Resume Builder System

A guided, supportive, production-ready registration and resume creation system for healthcare/paramedical students at LDM College. Designed for students weak in English — simple, step-by-step, warm in tone.

## Stitch UI Designs Generated

Three screens have been designed and are ready to guide implementation:

