## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **SMTP Configuration needed**: The email OTP system uses Hostinger SMTP. Please confirm these env variable names (or provide the correct values) so I can configure `nodemailer`:
> ```
> SMTP_HOST=smtp.hostinger.com
> SMTP_PORT=465
> SMTP_USER=noreply@yourdomain.com
> SMTP_PASS=your_smtp_password
> SMTP_FROM="LDM College <noreply@yourdomain.com>"
> ```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Attendance by Photo**: The user requested "attendance by taking picture" — this is a separate, complex feature (camera capture + face recognition or simple selfie log). This plan does **not** include it in this phase. It will need a separate implementation plan. Shall I include it now or keep it for Phase 2?

---

## Verification Plan

### TypeScript Build Check
```bash
cd "/media/swastik/focus/ldm feb"
npm run build
```
Expected: zero TypeScript errors.

### Manual Verification Flow
1. Visit `http://localhost:3000/register`
2. Fill in Step 1 (Basic Details) → click Continue
3. Fill in Step 2 (Academic Details) → click Continue
4. Check email inbox → enter the 6-digit OTP
5. See the success screen → click "Go to Dashboard"
6. On student dashboard, click "Resume Builder"
7. Fill each accordion section → click "Preview My Resume"
8. On preview page, verify resume looks correct → click "Download as PDF"
9. Open downloaded PDF → verify formatting is A4 and professional

### OTP Security Tests (Manual)
- Try entering wrong OTP 3 times → should be locked out
- Try resending OTP before 60 seconds → should be rate-limited
- Wait 6 minutes → OTP should be auto-expired (try to verify → rejected)
